{"arkId":"cl010358006","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010358006","modified ":"2026-02-24","title":"Harnachement de cheval de selle","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"Harnachement"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Selle turque"},{"type":"Titre","value":"Harnachement de cheval de selle"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : XVIIIe si\u00e8cle (1700 - 1800)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MS 231","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"BJ 202","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"26, 27, 28 ou 29","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"5169","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"},{"value":"ca 71","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts de l\u0027Islam","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Harnachement complet de cheval de selle : tapis, selle, mors, t\u00e9ti\u00e8re, \u00e9triers. Selle recouverte de laine lie de vin. Une large plaque de cuivre dor\u00e9 enveloppe le devant et l\u0027arri\u00e8re de la selle ; sur cette plaque : lapis et coraux de formes circulaires et ovales, alternant entre eux et pos\u00e9s par groupes que s\u00e9parent des appliques d\u0027or cisel\u00e9s dont les ornements se d\u00e9tachent sur fond d\u0027\u00e9mail bleu. Les m\u00eames coraux, les m\u00eames lapis, se retrouvent sur l\u0027\u00e9quipement de la t\u00eate et sur presque toute l\u0027\u00e9tendue du tapis, constituant une sorte de r\u00e9seau tr\u00e8s serr\u00e9, sur la t\u00eati\u00e8re, et cloisonn\u00e9 sur la housse par des lignes en losange de clous dor\u00e9s. Une \u00e9toffe d\u0027or recouvre la selle ; une \u00e9toffe de soie, d\u0027or et d\u0027argent est pos\u00e9e au milieu du tapis. Des franges d\u0027or tombent du frontal et entourent la housse. D\u00e9cor persan.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,61","displayDimension":"1,61 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"72","displayDimension":"72 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"2,3","displayDimension":"2,3 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : Composite (\u00e9mail bleu), M\u00e9tal (cuivre), M\u00e9tal (or), M\u00e9tal (argent), Mat\u00e9riau d\u0027origine animale (coraux), Lapis-Lazuli (Pierres fines) (lapis), Textile (laine lie de vin), Textile (soie)\r\nMat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Ciselure ; cloisonn\u00e9","placeOfCreation":"Bursa (=Brousse) (Asie Mineure et Europe orientale-\u003ETurquie) (?) ; Iran (Monde iranien - Caucase) (?) (Perse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"\u00c9gypte (Proche-Orient arabe) (?)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Etat major de l\u0027arm\u00e9e fran\u00e7aise","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de donation","value":"1798","startYear":1798,"endYear":1798}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, AI, Paris","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e de l\u0027Arm\u00e9e Invalides, Paris","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"place":[{"value":"Bursa (=Brousse)"},{"value":"Iran"},{"value":"\u00c9gypte"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000358006\/0001161318_OG.JPG","urlThumbna